description: Candie's Onolicious Grindz is bringing Filipino food to the streets of Mililani! They're serving up delicious Lechon, Furikake Chicken, Pork Adobo, and more! Pacific Island cuisine to make you feel serene is perfect for any occasion. Whether you need great food on the go, or want to feed your next big event, Candie's Onolicious Grindz is the perfect truck for you!
name: Candie's Onolicious Grindz
